{"title_page": "Municipality of Metlika", "text_new": "{{short description|Municipality of Slovenia}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n| name                    = Municipality of Metlika\n| native_name             = ''Ob\u010dina Metlika''\n| native_name_lang        = sl\n| settlement_type         = [[Municipalities of Slovenia|Municipality]]\n| image_skyline           = Metlika.JPG\n| image_alt               =\n| image_caption           =\n| image_shield            = Metlika.png\n| shield_size             = 120x80px\n| nickname                =\n| motto                   =\n| image_map               = Obcine Slovenija 2006 Metlika.svg\n| map_alt                 =\n| map_caption             = Location of the Municipality of Metlika in Slovenia\n| pushpin_map             = \n| pushpin_label_position  =\n| pushpin_map_alt         =\n| pushpin_map_caption     = \n| coordinates             = {{coord|45|39|N|15|19|E|region:SI_type:city|display=inline,title}}\n| coor_pinpoint           =\n| coordinates_footnotes   =\n| subdivision_type        = [[List of sovereign states|Country]]\n| subdivision_name        = {{flag|Slovenia}}\n| established_title       =\n| established_date        =\n| founder                 =\n| seat_type               = <!-- [[Capital (political)|Capital]] -->\n| seat                    =\n| government_footnotes    =\n| leader_party            =\n| leader_title            = [[Mayor]]\n| leader_name             = Darko Zevnik\n| unit_pref               = Metric<!-- or US or UK -->\n| area_footnotes          =<ref name=\"SURS\">{{cite web |title=Ob\u010dina Metlika |url=https://www.stat.si/obcine/sl/2016/Municip/Index/98 |website=Statisti\u010dni urad Republike Slovenije |accessdate=February 28, 2020}}</ref>\n| total_type              =\n| area_total_km2          = 108.9\n| area_note               =\n| elevation_footnotes     =\n| elevation_m             =\n| population_footnotes    = <ref name=\"SURS\"/>\n| population_total        = 8354\n| population_as_of        = 2016\n| population_density_km2  = auto\n| population_demonym      =\n| population_note         =\n| timezone1               = [[Central European Time|CET]]\n| utc_offset1             = +01\n| timezone1_DST           = [[Central European Summer Time|CEST]]\n| utc_offset1_DST         = +02\n| postal_code_type        =\n| postal_code             =\n| area_code_type          =\n| area_code               =\n| iso_code                =\n| website                 = {{Official URL}}\n| footnotes               =\n}}\n\nThe '''Municipality of Metlika''' ({{IPA-sl|m\u025b\u02c8tli\u02d0ka|pron|Sl-Metlika.ogg}}; {{lang-sl|Ob\u010dina Metlika}}) is a [[municipality]] in the traditional region of [[Lower Carniola]] in southeastern [[Slovenia]]. The seat of the municipality is the town of [[Metlika]]. Metlika became a municipality in 1994.<ref>{{cite book |title=Vzpostavitev lokalne samouprave v Republiki Sloveniji v \u0161tevilkah |date=2007 |publisher=Statisti\u010dni urad Republike Slovenije |location=Ljubljana |page=80|url=https://www.stat.si/StatWeb/File/DocSysFile/1290 |accessdate=February 28, 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Settlements==\nIn addition to the municipal seat of Metlika, the municipality also includes the following settlements:\n{{Div col|colwidth=14em}}\n* [[Bere\u010da Vas]]\n* [[Boginja Vas]]\n* [[Bojanja Vas]]\n* [[Boldra\u017e]]\n* [[Bor\u0161t, Metlika|Bor\u0161t]]\n* [[Bo\u017eakovo]]\n* [[Bo\u017ei\u010d Vrh]]\n* [[Brezovica pri Metliki]]\n* [[Bu\u0161inja Vas]]\n* [[\u010curile]]\n* [[Dole, Metlika|Dole]]\n* [[Dolnja Lokvica]]\n* [[Dolnje Dobravice]]\n* [[Dolnji Suhor pri Metliki]]\n* [[Drage, Metlika|Drage]]\n* [[Dragomlja Vas]]\n* [[Dra\u0161i\u010di]]\n* [[Ger\u0161i\u010di]]\n* [[Gornja Lokvica]]\n* [[Gornje Dobravice]]\n* [[Gornji Suhor pri Metliki]]\n* [[Grabrovec, Metlika|Grabrovec]]\n* [[Gradac, Metlika|Gradac]]\n* [[Grm pri Podzemlju]]\n* [[Hrast pri Jugorju]]\n* [[Jugorje pri Metliki]]\n* [[Kamenica, Metlika|Kamenica]]\n* [[Kaplji\u0161\u010de]]\n* [[Klo\u0161ter]]\n* [[Krasinec]]\n* [[Kra\u0161nji Vrh]]\n* [[Krivoglavice]]\n* [[Kri\u017eevska Vas, Metlika|Kri\u017eevska Vas]]\n* [[Krma\u010dina]]\n* [[Ma\u010dkovec pri Suhorju]]\n* [[Malo Le\u0161\u010de]]\n* [[Mlake, Metlika|Mlake]]\n* [[Okljuka]]\n* [[Otok, Metlika|Otok]]\n* [[Podzemelj]]\n* [[Prilozje]]\n* [[Primostek]]\n* [[Rado\u0161i, Metlika|Rado\u0161i]]\n* [[Radovica]]\n* [[Radovi\u010di]]\n* [[Rakovec, Metlika|Rakovec]]\n* [[Ravnace]]\n* [[Rosalnice]]\n* [[Sela pri Jugorju]]\n* [[\u0160kemljevec]]\n* [[\u0160krilje, Metlika|\u0160krilje]]\n* [[Slamna Vas]]\n* [[Svr\u017eaki]]\n* [[Trnovec, Metlika|Trnovec]]\n* [[Vido\u0161i\u010di]]\n* [[\u017delebej]]\n* [[\u017delezniki, Metlika|\u017delezniki]]\n* [[Zemelj]]\n{{Div col end}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{commons category-inline}}\n*[http://www.geopedia.si/#T105_F408:73_x524235.79650000005_y56135.2555_s12_b4 Municipality of Metlika on Geopedia]\n*[https://www.metlika.si/ Metlika municipal site]\n\n{{Geographic location\n | Centre = Metlika\n | N  = [[City Municipality of Novo Mesto|Novo Mesto]]\n | NE = {{flagicon|Croatia}} [[Ozalj]]\n | E  = {{flagicon|Croatia}} [[Kamanje]]<br/>{{flagicon|Croatia}} [[\u017dakanje]]\n | S  = [[Municipality of \u010crnomelj|\u010crnomelj]]\n | W  = [[Municipality of Semi\u010d|Semi\u010d]]\n}}\n{{Metlika}}\n{{Municipalities of Slovenia}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Municipality of Metlika}}\n[[Category:Municipalities in Lower Carniola|Metlika]]\n[[Category:Municipalities of Slovenia|Metlika]]\n[[Category:1994 establishments in Slovenia]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n| name                    = Municipality of Metlika\n| native_name             = ''Ob\u010dina Metlika''\n| native_name_lang        = sl\n| settlement_type         = [[Municipalities of Slovenia|Municipality]]\n| image_skyline           = Metlika.JPG\n| image_alt               =\n| image_caption           =\n| image_shield            = Metlika.png\n| shield_size             = 120